{"tid":2268330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"WHO 譚德塞宣佈自我隔離","createTime":"2020-11-02T16:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T01:52:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8f505d72c4d67ec28df9a2beabc4b6b2a20454ba","tid":2268330,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img3.secretchina.com/pic/2020/5-19/p2692631a596717757-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg3.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2020%2F5-19%2Fp2692631a596717757-ss.jpg&h=a90d7856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片來源：FABRICE COFFRINI/AFP via Getty Images）<br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織（WHO）總幹事譚德塞11月1日在推特發布消息，確認他曾接觸過中共病毒(又稱新冠狀病毒，COVID-19)確診者。他表示，自己沒有出現相關症狀，未來幾天會自我隔離，遵守世界衛生組織（WHO）協議並在家工作。<br />\n<br />\n1日（週一）晚上，譚德塞在推特上發文說，他接觸了一個COVID-19病毒（中共病毒）檢測呈陽性者，稱目前自己的健康狀況「良好」，沒有任何症狀。這位現年55歲的衣索比亞人在推特上繼續寫道：根據世衛組織的規定，未來幾天，他將繼續進行隔離並在家中工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2020/11/03/951221.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2020%2F11%2F03%2F951221.html&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=96ca39c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2020/11/03/951221.html</a>"},{"pid":"dceff00599823cedf9fb91320f0d465ea5c7654b","tid":2268330,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"karma is a bitch <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ca57c74a5af035ba59ea57772c06e065489432","tid":2268330,"uid":344679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:57:30.000Z","msg":"食屎啦談得菜"},{"pid":"6ac5ff145bcab53ffff813519471d290fcb9b85e","tid":2268330,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/